msg = '\r\n\r\nSo now enter the cassette tapes menu then use the "Staff Divisions Hook" '
.. 'to set all divisions to max, make sure to change the flag from the default to '
.. '"All Divisions" if you want to unlock every thing. Then enable the "Staff Hook" '
.. '(make sure to change the view if needed so the addresses will populate). '
.. 'Now go to the R&amp;D unit and enable the "Staff Tweaker Hook", then enable the '
.. '"Setup Specialists" option (disabled by default), now just scroll down in the R&amp;D '
.. 'unit to get one of all the sepcialists. '
.. 'Then "Auto Assign" all staff to have the changes take effect. And this should unlock '
.. 'every thing in the development section. And you may need to add the needed GMP and '
.. 'resourses. Have fun and enjoy.\r\n'
.. '* Note: The "Drug Developer" will be in the wrong unit, so until you unlock the medical '
.. 'unit you won\'t be able to fully develop the drugs.\r\n'
.. '* Note: At the start of the game all staff are "Special Characters" and the '
.. '"Staff Tweaker Hook" has a "No Editing Special Characters" option that is enabled by '
.. 'default.\r\n'
.. '* Note: The "Bionic Arm" tab isn\'t avalable until the mission freeing the developer is '
.. 'completed.\r\n'
.. 'You can leave this message open to help.\r\n\r\n'
print(msg)
